y the Douro Valley has on offer! Twisting roads snake their way up between vineyards and mountains to panoramic viewpoints across Portugal and Spain.&#xA0;We think this is one of the unique places to see in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Europe<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/travel-portugal-campervan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to travel Portugal by Campervan<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103406\/douro-valley-portugal-scenic-roads.jpg\" alt=\"douro valley portugal scenic roads\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"311\" alt=\"douro valley portugal scenic roads\" class=\"wp-image-52007 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103406\/douro-valley-portugal-scenic-roads.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103406\/douro-valley-portugal-scenic-roads-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103406\/douro-valley-portugal-scenic-roads-600x414.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103406\/douro-valley-portugal-scenic-roads-800x552.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltino