om\/maps\/dir\/Peso+da+R%C3%A9gua,+Portugal\/Pinh%C3%A3o,+Portugal\/@41.1649966,-7.7283934,12z\/data=!3m1!4b1!4m14!4m13!1m5!1m1!1s0xd3b4d444ba6dd43:0x400ebbde4903ca0!2m2!1d-7.7867018!2d41.1656737!1m5!1m1!1s0xd3b5b4a79d9197d:0x9f06373ba234c06e!2m2!1d-7.5328476!2d41.1874919!3e0?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Peso de Regua and Pinhao<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-viewpoints\">Viewpoints<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to keep your eye out for multiple amazing viewpoints. For example, S&#xE3;o Leonardo da Galafura, the most famous viewpoint in the region, sitting above patterned vineyards and the Douro River. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another great viewpoint is the &#x2018;Double Viewpoint De Loivos&#x2019; <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/icdHFsskuefcy8Jz9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">located here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103323\/duory-valley-portugal-viewpoint.jpg\" alt=\"duoro valley portugal viewpoint\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"duoro valley portugal viewpoint\" class=\"wp-image-52887 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103323\/duory-valley-portugal-viewpoint.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103323\/duory-valley-portugal-viewpoint-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103323\/duory-valley-portugal-viewpoint-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103323\/duory-valley-portugal-viewpoint-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103323\/d