 the beauty of the region.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Temperatures can be very high in the summer, so it&#x2019;s recommended to enjoy hiking in the cooler temperatures of the spring or the fall.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>See all <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/booking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">places to overnight on Booking.com<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-discover-the-douro-river\"><strong>Discover the Douro River<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The heart of the Douro valley is the great Douro River itself. The perfect way to enjoy the views from the water is by taking a boat trip, or by kayaking. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many of the wine tours from Porto often include a boat tour. However, if you are doing a self-guided itinerary, there are many great options to enjoy the river. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/porto-duoro-wine-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all Douro tours here<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/porto-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The ultimate city trip to Porto, Portugal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"douro valley portugal river\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"douro valley portugal river\" class=\"wp-image-52006 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103410\/douro-valley-portugal-river-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202